candidates.stmt:
We, by which I mean ALL of us, can only succeed by working together and respecting each others' diverse cultures and views. Diversity, in all of its forms, is a wonderful resource, to be celebrated, that makes us and our society special.

Important to me personally is:
1. Protecting our beautiful world, at all levels: international, national and local;
2. Rebuilding much stronger links with Europe;
3. Improving, dramatically, our NHS; and creating a National Social Care Service, especially for the elderly and others who need help to live decent lives

And if all this means paying a bit more tax, so be it!
